Subject: FEATURE: add support for ordering LPN transforms
Date: Thu, 23 Sep 2010 08:57:02 -0600
X-Mailer: Apple Mail (2.936)

Change abstraction list in property file to the form:

lpn.abstraction.method.n.m=<method name>

n = 1 : preprocess
n = 2 : main loop
n = 3 : postprocess

m is the order that it is applied

Leverage the gui for reb2sac to abstractions to set this order.

Change the abstraction loop to use this order.

Do not put LPN abstractions into the simulation property file when it  
is not starting with an LPN model.

